    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-mint condition, having been preserved with the utmost care. From its flawless paint to the pristine interior that still feels brand new, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly immaculate example that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
